text: Saleh Ahmed (born 21 July 1997) is a first-class and List A cricketer from Bangladesh. In December 2015 he was named in Bangladesh's squad for the 2016 Under-19 Cricket World Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Barisal Division cricketers Category:Old DOHS Sports Club cricketers Category:Cricket Coaching School cricketers Category:Bangladesh under-19 cricketers
